          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Slide 2 -->
        <div class="carousel-item" style="background-image:  url('/images/image2.jpg')">
          <div class="carousel-container">
            <div class="container">
              <h2 class="animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">We value our customers</h2>
              <p class="animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">A customer is the most important visitor on our premises. He is not dependent on us. We are dependent on him. He is not an interruption in our work. He is the purpose of it.</p>
